Sentencas: A perovskite-based electrolyte, Ca-substituted YAlO3, has been synthesized by the citrate gel process.
Titulo: A novel perovskite-based proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The conductivity of Y0.9Ca0.1AlO3-delta has been studied by AC impedance spectroscopy in controlled atmospheres in the temperature range 300-800 degrees C.
Titulo: A novel perovskite-based proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The material has been found to be a mixed conductor with dominant p-type electronic conduction at elevated temperatures and a combined protonic conduction below 600 degrees C in wet conditions.
Titulo: A novel perovskite-based proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The H/D isotope effect on conductivity confirms the presence of protonic conductivity between 400 and 600 degrees C. (C) 2012 Acta Materialia Inc.
Titulo: A novel perovskite-based proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells
